description.en: E-LEVEN TOKEN (ELV) a token developed by the e-leven group, With a fixed supply of 11 million Tokens, E-LEVEN (ELV) integrates what we will henceforth call Crypto Stock Market. E-leven (ELV) is presented as the solution to the excessive commissions that Brokers charge when receiving Cryptocurrencies from investors or Traders who come to seek a competitive, supportive, fair and transparent scenario.
